summary:
I‚Äôm a passionate and enthusiastic UI/UX and Product Designer with 4 years of experience based in Amsterdam.

With an MSc degree in Interaction Design, I learned a great deal about human-computer interaction and how a simple but thoughtful design change can significantly impact perception and usability. My engineering background taught me to pay attention to details.

I love designing as much as understanding customer needs and converting them to design specifications.

My past experience taught me about team building and project/time management which helps me to enhance my design process and I used it to build effective Design Systems, User Interface Design, User Experience Design, Accessibility, User flow, User Research & User testing.


I look forward to talking to you, just drop me a message if you would like to chat!
